<div id="fb_body_wrapper">
<div id="fb_tab">
<div id="fb_tab_l">Local</div>
<div id="fb_tab_r">&nbsp;<img src="images/fblogo_mini.gif" /></div> 
</div> 
<div id="fb_pg_wrapper">
<div id="fb_pg_body">
	Instruction de gestion des erreurs pour d&eacute;finir le gestionnaire d'erreur courant<br \>
<br \>
<div class="fb_sect_title">Syntaxe</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
On <b>Local</b> Error Goto <i>label</i><br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Usage</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
On <b>Local</b> Error Goto <i>label</i><br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Param&eacute;tres</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><i>label</i></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">label o&ugrave; sauter en cas d'erreur<br \>
<br \>
</div></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Description</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
La clause <tt><b>Local</b></tt> dans une construction de type <tt><a href="KeyPgOnerror.html">On Error</a></tt> permet de d&eacute;finir un gestionnaire d'erreur dans le m&ecirc;me style <tt><a href="KeyPgSub.html">Sub</a></tt>/<tt><a href="KeyPgFunction.html">Function</a></tt> que <tt><b>On Local Error</b></tt>. <tt><a href="KeyPgExit.html">Exit</a></tt> <tt><a href="KeyPgSub.html">Sub</a></tt>/<tt><a href="KeyPgFunction.html">Function</a></tt> doit &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute; avant le d&eacute;but du gestionnaire d'erreur.<br \>
<br \>
Notez que le programme doit &ecirc;tre compil&eacute; avec l'option <i><a href="CompilerOpte.html">-e</a></i> ou <i><a href="CompilerOptex.html">-ex</a></i> pour que fonctionne la gestion de type QB des erreurs.<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Exemple</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><div class="freebasic">
<span class="com">''&nbsp;compile&nbsp;with&nbsp;-lang&nbsp;fblite&nbsp;or&nbsp;qb</span><br />
<br />
<span class="def">#lang&nbsp;"fblite"<br />
</span><br />
<span class="key">Declare</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Sub</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">foo</span><br />
<br />
<span class="wrd">foo</span><br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"ok"</span><br />
<span class="key">Sleep</span><br />
<br />
<span class="key">Sub</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">foo</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">Dim</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">errno</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">As</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Integer</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">On</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Local</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Error</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Goto</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">fail</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">Open</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"xzxwz.zwz"</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">For</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Input</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">As</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">#</span><span class="num">1</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">On</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Local</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Error</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Goto</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">Exit</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Sub</span><br />
<span class="wrd">fail</span><span class="oth">:</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="com">'&nbsp;here&nbsp;starts&nbsp;the&nbsp;error&nbsp;handler</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="wrd">errno</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Err</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"Error&nbsp;"</span><span class="oth">;</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">errno</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="com">'&nbsp;just&nbsp;print&nbsp;the&nbsp;error&nbsp;number</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">Sleep</span><br />
<span class="key">End</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Sub</span><br />
</div></tt><br />
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Diff&eacute;rences avec QB</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> La clause LOCAL vient de PDS 7.1. QB 4.5 ne permet pas la gestion locale des erreurs.<br \>
<br \>
</ul></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Voir aussi</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> <a href="ProPgErrorHandling.html">Gestion des erreurs</a><br \>
<br \>
</ul><br \>
</div>
</div>
</div> 
